SCN mwSpellDivineInterventionScript

; Casting in Morrowind takes you to nearest shrine
; Casting in Cyrodiil takes you to nearest major city chapel
; Casting in Shivering Isles has no effect

float dist1
float dist2
float dist3
float dist4
float dist5
float dist6
float dist7
float dist8
float distance
short destination

Begin ScriptEffectStart
	if PlayerInMorrowind == 1
		set dist1 to fbmwDivineMournhold.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist2 to fbmwDivineWolverineHall.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist3 to fbmwDivineEbonheart.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist4 to fbmwDivinePelagiad.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist5 to fbmwDivineMoonmoth.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist6 to fbmwDivineBuckmoth.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist7 to fbmwDivineGnisis.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist8 to fbmwDivineFrostmoth.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
	elseif GetPlayerInSEWorld != 1
		set dist1 to AnvilStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist2 to BravilStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist3 to BrumaStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist4 to CheydinhalStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist5 to ChorrolStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist6 to ICStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist7 to LeyawiinStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
		set dist8 to SkingradStablesMapMarker.GetDistance fbmwInterventionMarker
	endif
End



Begin ScriptEffectFinish

	if Player.GetInCell SothaSSil
		Message "Teleportation magic doesn't work in this place"
		return
	endif

	if GetStage fbmwTRSothaSil == 100
		Message "You feel a powerful force interrupt your spell."
		return
	endif

	if GetPlayerInSEWorld == 1
		Message "You are beyond the Divines' reach."
		Return
	endif

	set distance to dist1
	set destination to 1
	if (dist2 < distance)
		set distance to dist2
		set destination to 2
	endif
	if (dist3 < distance)
		set distance to dist3
		set destination to 3
	endif
	if (dist4 < distance)
		set distance to dist4
		set destination to 4
	endif
	if (dist5 < distance)
		set distance to dist5
		set destination to 5
	endif
	if (dist6 < distance)
		set destination to 6
	endif
	if (dist7 < distance)
		set destination to 7
	endif
	if (dist8 < distance)
		set destination to 8
	endif

	if PlayerInMorrowind == 1
		if (destination == 1)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineMournhold
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineMournhold
		elseif (destination == 2)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineWolverineHall
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineWolverineHall
		elseif (destination == 3)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineEbonheart
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineEbonheart
		elseif (destination == 4)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivinePelagiad
			Player.moveto fbmwDivinePelagiad
		elseif (destination == 5)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineMoonmoth
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineMoonmoth
		elseif (destination == 6)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineBuckmoth
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineBuckmoth
		elseif (destination == 7)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineGnisis
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineGnisis
		elseif (destination == 8)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto fbmwDivineFrostmoth
			Player.moveto fbmwDivineFrostmoth
		endif
	else
		if (destination == 1)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto AnvilBeggarAtChurch
			Player.moveto AnvilBeggarAtChurch
		elseif (destination == 2)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto BravilCathedralMarker
			Player.moveto BravilCathedralMarker
		elseif (destination == 3)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto BrumaChapelStepsMarker
			Player.moveto BrumaChapelStepsMarker
		elseif (destination == 4)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto CheydinhalChapel
			Player.moveto CheydinhalChapel
		elseif (destination == 5)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto ChorrolChapelMarker
			Player.moveto ChorrolChapelMarker
		elseif (destination == 6)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto ICTempleCenterMarker
			Player.moveto ICTempleCenterMarker
		elseif (destination == 7)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto LeyawiinChapelStepsMarker
			Player.moveto LeyawiinChapelStepsMarker
		elseif (destination == 8)
			fbmwInterventionMarker.moveto SkingradChapelStepsMarker
			Player.moveto SkingradChapelStepsMarker
		endif
	endif

End
